Tipos de STORAGE
________________
DAS  -> Direct Attach Storage
NAS  -> NetWork Attach Storage
SAN  -> Storage Area Network (Fibra)

|--------------------|
|                    |
|                    |
|  |---|   |---|     |                         |-----------|
|                    |                         |           |
|                    |                         |           | 
|  |---|   |---|     | TCP/IP    (Nivel 3)     |           |
|  |---|   |---|     |<---------------------   |           |
|                    |      FTP                |           |
|  |---|   |---|     |      Samba/SMB          |           |
|  |---|   |---|     |      NFS                |           |
|                    |                         -------------
|--------------------|


